Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜心你所居住的武藏野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个四处都很平坦的国度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉 好像明白了阿尔法所说的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我驰过这一带 就突然明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像身体中某个从未使用的部分被开启了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.71,0:02:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片水域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是蜿蜒至山谷深处的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常独自来到这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.62,0:03:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会想到很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:04:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者什么也不去想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.04,0:05:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是由声音和气味构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是比喻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店已经相当破旧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该上漆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油漆很贵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没客人光顾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.89,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}现在是晚间气象预报时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.43,0:10:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}我目前位于台风“梅花”的中心附近上空
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}接下来我们“滨松气象直击”节目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}将会在第一时间为您报道台风的最新动态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}据投下的计测器传来的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}现在 台风的中心气压为905千帕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}中心最大风速为秒速10米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.87,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把重要的东西带上 今天就去我的加油站睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是让…我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs24}（供应汽油）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就这样 我还得回家做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.28,0:17:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家… 究竟怎样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店的玻璃 相当危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有窗户…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 把招牌留在外头了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.02,0:18:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～开始觉得不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.78,0:18:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台风怎么还不离开呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}由湘南登陆的台风“梅花”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}径直扫过平原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}经由茨城国往鹿岛滩出海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{{\i1\fs24}本次台风似乎在各地均造成了相当程度的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.91,0:19:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24}但目前我们尚未获知详情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\fs24\fad(0,100)}此外 本次我们节目…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的店子…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想它已经很努力地挣扎过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.10,0:23:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为它原本就很破旧了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天看你相当从容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.07,0:23:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.00,0:23:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大伯你来之前我还很是震惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.31,0:23:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足足有一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.87,0:24:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.48,0:24:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 这家店暂时还能维持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.49,0:24:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一直放晴的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.45,0:24:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 高广自那以后怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我想他应该很难熬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.08,0:24:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对高广来说\N这是他头一次无法看到自己熟悉的景色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.45,0:24:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我… 想暂时外出走走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.31,0:24:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出挣钱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.98,0:24:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 算是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去四处看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这次我想 比以往游荡得更远些
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:24:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.47,0:25:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出游荡的时候要小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.05,0:25:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.06,0:25:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.03,0:25:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 我会让这家店恢复原貌
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.23,0:25:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要再来一杯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.84,0:25:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 还没喝完
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.45,0:25:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔法 你不骑摩托车去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.43,0:25:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不一定到处都有加油站的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.10,0:25:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 在外出的期间我想把摩托车交由你保管
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.74,0:25:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.92,0:25:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我能驾驶得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.48,0:25:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该很容易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.84,0:25:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高广你也快和我一样高了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.64,0:26:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.07,0:26:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次见面的时候 你一定会比我高了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.94,0:26:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿我向你请教驾驶的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.10,0:26:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.09,0:26:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.88,0:26:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.28,0:26:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿就好
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.90,0:26:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.39,0:31:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高广
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.67,0:31:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 麻卉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.19,0:31:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.08,0:31:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝咖啡吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.38,0:31:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.50,0:31:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.82,0:31:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你喝剩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.81,0:31:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.99,0:31:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.25,0:31:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.72,0:31:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.20,0:31:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气已经很冷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.87,0:31:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.66,0:31:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高广
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.19,0:31:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.73,0:31:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心阿尔法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.53,0:31:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.18,0:27:44.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}徘徊游荡  徘徊游荡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.64,0:27:51.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}此刻我正出外游走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.17,0:27:59.40,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}你现在可好？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.80,0:28:06.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}向久违的你道声抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.23,0:28:20.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}只需稍稍绕过日常
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.62,0:28:25.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}遥遥归乡路
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.41,0:28:36.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}寻觅着我的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.59,0:28:40.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}遥遥归乡路
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.58,0:28:43.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}向着南方前行
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.19,0:28:50.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}定会走向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.16,0:29:02.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}徘徊游荡  徘徊游荡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.35,0:29:10.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}我想趋近前方
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.99,0:29:17.72,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}去往湖边  去往森林
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.96,0:29:25.02,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}世界就像黄昏的山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.36,0:29:28.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}遥遥归乡路
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.26,0:29:33.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}我的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.36,0:29:39.35,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}洋溢着妙不可言的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.38,0:29:43.93,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}遥遥归乡路
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.25,0:29:47.73,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}能够确信的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.02,0:29:54.41,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}便是如此普通的事
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.41,0:30:13.90,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}遥遥归乡路
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.21,0:30:25.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}寻觅着我的归所
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.37,0:30:28.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}遥遥归乡路
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.25,0:30:32.68,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}将我所拍下的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.02,0:30:39.57,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,500)}诚心诚意展现给你
